Here's a PlantUML component diagram capturing the static architecture of the HRM Virtual Machine project, focusing on the general architectural concern:

```plantuml
@startuml SV-97_HumanResourceMachine

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Python>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Rust>> LightGreen
}

[HRM Assembly Code] as AssemblyCode

package "HRM Virtual Machine" {
  [Tokenizer] as Tokenizer
  [Translator/Assembler] as Translator
  [Bytecode Disassembler] as Disassembler
  [Virtual Machine] as VM
  [Logger] as Logger

  component "Python Implementation" <<Python>> {
    [Python Tokenizer] as PyTokenizer
    [Python Translator] as PyTranslator
    [Python Disassembler] as PyDisassembler
    [Python VM] as PyVM
  }

  component "Rust Implementation" <<Rust>> {
    [Rust Tokenizer] as RustTokenizer
    [Rust Translator] as RustTranslator
    [Rust Disassembler] as RustDisassembler
    [Rust VM] as RustVM
  }
}

AssemblyCode --> Tokenizer
Tokenizer --> Translator
Translator --> VM
VM --> Disassembler

Tokenizer ..> PyTokenizer
Tokenizer ..> RustTokenizer
Translator ..> PyTranslator
Translator ..> RustTranslator
Disassembler ..> PyDisassembler
Disassembler ..> RustDisassembler
VM ..> PyVM
VM ..> RustVM

RustTokenizer --> Logger
RustTranslator --> Logger
RustDisassembler --> Logger
RustVM --> Logger

@enduml
```